if it couldn't die, Paul.

51:55.534 --> 52:00.534
Would you be?

52:02.708 --> 52:07.378
We're something this thing
has never dealt with before.

52:07.379 --> 52:12.379
What?

52:16.722 --> 52:21.392
We're brothers.

52:21.393 --> 52:24.479
Oh, shit.

52:24.480 --> 52:25.855
Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!

52:25.856 --> 52:28.649
Uh, Neal, dear?

52:28.650 --> 52:31.277
