right now, so, uh,

52:36.825 --> 52:37.909
put it down.

52:37.910 --> 52:39.202
I'll be fine.

52:39.203 --> 52:41.996
Put it down,

52:41.997 --> 52:46.250
please.

52:46.251 --> 52:50.088
[ Chainsaw thuds ]

52:50.089 --> 52:55.089
Come on, pal.

52:57.930 --> 52:59.013
Paulie?

52:59.014 --> 53:01.182
Sweetheart,

53:01.183 --> 53:02.892
please tell me what's going on.

53:02.893 --> 53:04.352
It's not a big deal.

53:04.353 --> 53:06.104
Well, if you can just tell me
a little bit, honey,

53:06.105 --> 53:10.858
maybe I can, I don't know,
somehow help you?

53:10.859 --> 53:15.859
If you want to help him,
stay out of his way.

54:02.744 --> 54:04.579
NEAL:
It looks pretty good in there.

54:04.580 --> 54:09.580
PAULIE: Yeah, not bad for two hours
of sleep between us.

54:27.227 --> 54:30.313
We're okay.

54:30.314 --> 54:34.317
Before I got sent away,
I used to sleep anywhere I could,

54:34.318 --> 54:36.694
like the kitchen,
Mom and Dad's room, outside.

54:36.695 --> 54:38.070
I slept in the garage
a few times,

54:38.071 --> 54:40.698
but it only ever got to me

54:40.699 --> 54:43.201
when I would
try to sleep in beds.

54:43.202 --> 54:46.954
It's bound to beds.

54:46.955 --> 54:48.414
Why?

54:48.415 --> 54:51.500
I don't know.

54:51.501 --> 54:53.544
I have theories, I guess.

54:53.545 --> 54:56.464
Beds are where people
sleep the most,

54:56.465 --> 54:58.257
so if it usually strikes
when you sleep,

54:58.258 --> 55:00.176
it makes sense.

55:00.177 --> 55:02.178
That's where you have
the most dreams

55:02.179 --> 55:04.305
and nightmares.

55:04.306 --> 55:06.599
Maybe that's what it looks for.

55:06.600 --> 55:10.186
Maybe.

55:10.187 --> 55:12.813
I have another theory, too,

55:12.814 --> 55:15.900
but you can't freak out.

55:15.901 --> 55:20.071
Go ahead.

55:20.072 --> 55:21.906
I read once that you shed

55:21.907 --> 55:24.492
